<span class="title">سورة الفجر</span>
قال ابن الجزري:
<span class="red">...............</span> <span class="red">...</span>
~~<span class="red">.........</span> وكسر الوتر رد
فتى <span class="red">............</span> <span class="red">...</span>
~~<span class="red">...............</span>
